sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant ListingService
    participant DynamoDB
    participant EventBridge

    Client->>ListingService: POST /v1/listings
    ListingService->>ListingService: Extract ownerId from Cognito JWT
    ListingService->>DynamoDB: Save listing
    ListingService->>EventBridge: Publish listing.created
    ListingService-->>Client: 201 Created